'''插電式混合動力車'''（{{lang-en|'''p'''lug-in '''h'''ybrid '''e'''lectric '''v'''ehicle}}，常缩写為'''PHEV'''），簡稱'''插电混动车'''或'''插混車'''，是一種[[混合動力車輛|混合動力車輛]]。與一般混合動力車輛比較，PHEV的特徵在於其[[充電電池|充電電池]]除了可由車輛上的[[內燃機|內燃機]]所驅動的[[發電機|發電機]]充電外，也可以使用外部電源充電。一般而言，PHEV的電池容量比[[純電動車|純電動車]]小，但大多大於普通油電混合動力車的電池容量。

==性能==
插電式混合動力車輛是針對通勤族設計的，多數通勤族通勤距離在十幾公里內，插電式混合動力車輛的電池續航力只要有二三十公里即可以滿足多數通勤需求（通勤時不需啟動內燃機）。在長途駕駛（大多為假日出遊）的情況下，既使是續航力數百公里的電動車也可能沒電，此時插電式混合動力車輛則使用內燃機提供能量，方便性與傳統汽柴油車輛相近；引擎運轉模式更接近最高效率的定速運轉，因此也很省油，甚至可以讓[[轉子引擎|轉子引擎]]、[[渦輪引擎|渦輪引擎]]達到低油耗低污染的目標；有些車輛使用小型引擎、且不使用複雜的傳動系統，可以抵銷電池所增加的重量跟成本。

對於發電廠而言，插電式混合動力車輛大多是在離峰時間充電，此特性讓發配電業者幾乎不需要花大錢擴充發電機組及[[電力網|電力網]]；而且電廠在離峰時間是處於低輸出低效率的運轉模式，此時若增加輸出，所增加的污染及碳排放特別少。如能配合智慧充電系統（車輛與電業溝通、決定充電時間），環保效益更佳。

而在整體污染排放方面，在電動車模式時，是把污染給轉移至電廠，電廠可以採用大型污染防治設備，因此整體污染排放更低，就算用燃煤發電廠發電也值得，而且電廠位於郊區，其空氣污染排放可以在大幅稀釋後才被人們吸入，同樣污染對人類健康的妨礙更低；而在啟動引擎時，污染排放也因為定速運轉而非常低，還是可以降低整體污染。至於在能源效率方面，由於大型發電廠的效率比汽車引擎高，又多在離峰時間充電，就算考慮電力傳輸儲存的損失，充電仍可提高整體能源效率。

插電式混合動力車輛的另一個可能發展是充當發電機，成為停電時的備援用電。但混合動力車的缺點，插電式混合動力車輛可能更嚴重，例如鋰礦問題、電池成本、製造電池的環境成本。

==历史==

===早期===
1899年生产的[[Lohner-Porsche|Lohner-Porsche]]是世界上第一款插電式混合動力車<ref name=HybridCarHist>{{cite web|url= http://www.hybridcars.com/history/history-of-hybrid-vehicles.html |title=History of Hybrid Vehicles |publisher=HybridCars.com |date=2006-03-27 |accessdate=2011-10-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904154040/http://www.hybridcars.com/history/history-of-hybrid-vehicles.html |archivedate=2009-09-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ultimatecarpage.com/car/3456/Lohner-Porsche-Mixte-Voiturette.html|title=Lohner-Porsche Mixte Voiturette|date=2007-11-19|publisher=Ultimate Car Page|accessdate=2011-10-25|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120119164407/http://www.ultimatecarpage.com/car/3456/Lohner-Porsche-Mixte-Voiturette.html|archive-date=2012-01-19}}</ref>。不过“插電式混合動力車”这个词本身是20世纪后半叶才出现的，发明者是[[加州大学戴维斯分校|加州大学戴维斯分校]]的安德鲁·弗兰克教授<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB113815056026555394 |title=Coalition Turns On to 'Plug-In Hybrids': Utilities, Localities, DaimlerChrysler Give Traction to Professor's Drive For High Mileage |newspaper=The Wall Street Journal |first=John J. |last=Fialka |date=2006-01-25 |accessdate=2011-06-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150404232000/http://www.wsj.com/articles/SB113815056026555394 |archive-date=2015-04-04  }}</ref>，他也因此被誉为“插電式混合動力車之父”。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.calcars.org/history.html|title=Plug-In Hybrids: State Of Play, History & Players|publisher=CalCars |accessdate=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150502064532/http://www.calcars.org/history.html|archive-date=2015-05-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://abcnews.go.com/print?id=5406454 |title=Can Plug-In Hybrids Ride to America's Rescue? |publisher=ABC News |first=Mark |last=Clayton |date=2008-07-19 |accessdate=2009-04-18 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080809164217/http://abcnews.go.com/print?id=5406454 |archive-date=2008-08-09  }}</ref><ref name="Plug_in">{{cite book |first=Sherry |last=Boschert |author-link=Sherry Boschert |title=Plug-in Hybrids: The Cars that will Recharge America |year=2006 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/pluginhybridscar00bosc/page/68 68–78] |publisher=New Society Publishers |location=Gabriola Island, Canada |isbn=978-0-86571-571-4 |url=https://archive.org/details/pluginhybridscar00bosc/page/68 }}</ref>
===量产===

2003年，[[雷诺|雷诺]]开始在欧洲销售插電式混合動力的[[雷诺Kangoo|雷诺Kangoo]]，即“Elect'road”<ref>{{cite web|last=Holinger |first=Heinrich |date=2003-10-11 |url= http://www.evworld.com/article.cfm?storyid=582 |title=Renault Electric Kangoo Can Do |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080205145932/http://evworld.com/article.cfm?storyid=582 |archivedate=2008-02-05 |work=EVWorld.com |accessdate=2019-10-22}}</ref>，但仅仅卖出500辆，在2007年停产。<ref name="kangoo">{{cite press release|work=Renault |date=March 10, 2003 |url= http://www.calcars.org/KangooRangeExtend.pdf |title=Kangoo reinvents the electric car |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20070412032635/http://www.calcars.org/KangooRangeExtend.pdf |archivedate=2007-04-12 |accessdate=2019-10-22}}</ref>

世界上正式量产的插電式混合動力車是中国的[[比亞迪F3DM|比亚迪F3DM]]，它在2008年12月15日开始在中国销售，不过它最初只提供给政府和公司<ref name=F3DM>Crippen, A. (December 15, 2008) [https://www.cnbc.com/id/28236421 "Warren Buffett's Electric Car Hits the Chinese Market, But Rollout Delayed For U.S. & Europe"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107113753/https://www.cnbc.com/id/28236421 |date=2017-11-07 }} ''CNBC''. Retrieved December 2008.</ref><ref name=bwf3dm>Balfour, F. (December 15, 2008) [http://www.businessweek.com/globalbiz/content/dec2008/gb20081215_913780.htm "China's First Plug-In Hybrid Car Rolls Out"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081220105009/http://www.businessweek.com/globalbiz/content/dec2008/gb20081215_913780.htm |date=2008-12-20 }}</ref><ref name=GCC1208>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2008/12/byd-f3dm-plug-i.html|title=BYD F3DM Plug-in Hybrid Goes On Sale in China|date=2008-12-15|publisher=Green Car Congress|accessdate=2009-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090304004900/http://www.greencarcongress.com/2008/12/byd-f3dm-plug-i.html|archive-date=2009-03-04}}</ref>。个人直到在2010年3月开始才能买到这款车<ref name=GCC0310>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2010/03/byd-20100323.html#more|title=BYD Auto To Begin Sales of F3DM Plug-in to Individuals|publisher=Green Car Congress|date=2010-03-23|accessdate=2010-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100326114129/http://www.greencarcongress.com/2010/03/byd-20100323.html#more|archive-date=2010-03-26}}</ref><ref name=Edmunds310>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.edmunds.com/greencaradvisor/2010/03/byd-auto-to-offer-f3dm-plug-in-hybrid-to-chinese-individuals-starting-next-week.html |title=BYD Auto to Offer F3DM Plug-in Hybrid to Chinese Individuals Starting Next Week |publisher=[[Edmunds.com|Edmunds.com]] |date=2010-03-23 |accessdate=2010-03-27  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100330091520/http://blogs.edmunds.com/greencaradvisor/2010/03/byd-auto-to-offer-f3dm-plug-in-hybrid-to-chinese-individuals-starting-next-week.html |archivedate=2010-03-30 }}</ref>。截止2017年末，市场上已有40多款插電式混合動力車<ref name=Top10PEVs2016>{{cite news | url=http://www.hybridcars.com/tesla-model-s-is-worlds-best-selling-plug-in-car-for-second-year-in-a-row/ | title=Tesla Model S Is World’s Best-Selling Plug-in Car For Second Year In A Row | first=Jeff | last=Cobb | website=HybridCars.com | date=2017-01-26 | accessdate=2017-01-26 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170126165815/http://www.hybridcars.com/tesla-model-s-is-worlds-best-selling-plug-in-car-for-second-year-in-a-row/ | archive-date=2017-01-26  }} ''See also detailed 2016 sales and cumulative global sales in the two graphs.''</ref>。{{As of|2018|12}}，全球的插電式混合動力車产量为180万台，而美国是最大的插電式混合動力車市场，中国和日本次之<ref name=Outlook2018>{{cite web |url=https://webstore.iea.org/download/direct/1045?fileName=Global_EV_Outlook_2018.pdf |title=Global EV Outlook 2017: 3 million and counting |author=International Energy Agency (IEA), Clean Energy Ministerial, and Electric Vehicles Initiative (EVI) |publisher=IEA Publications |date=May 2018 |accessdate=2018-12-16 |archive-date=2020-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616050109/https://webstore.iea.org/login?ReturnUrl=%2fdownload%2fdirect%2f1045%3ffilename%3dglobal_ev_outlook_2018.pdf&filename=global_ev_outlook_2018.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

